ilance for veterinary medicines\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003einspection of manufacturers, wholesale dealers and retailers of veterinary medicines\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eenforcement of legislation\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003esurveillance for residues of veterinary medicines and banned substances in livestock and animal products\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2014-08-14T16:09:06Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Director of Operations, VMD","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"84779692-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"\u003cp\u003eThe Director of Authorisations, VMD supports the chief executive officer with the day-to-day running of the VMD and leads on:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eassessment of applications, issuing and maintenance of Marketing Authorisation\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003elicensing of manufacturers and wholesale dealers of veterinary medicines\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003emanagement of the research and development programme on behalf of the policy customer\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eassessing applications for import and export certificates for veterinary medicines\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2015-02-04T11:44:52Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Interim Director of Authorisations, VMD","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"8477b772-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"\u003cp\u003eThe Chief Executive Officer, VMD provides support and advice to Defra Ministers, the Chief Operating Officer and the Chief Veterinary Officer where the regulation of veterinary medicines contributes to policy in respect of animal health and welfare. They’re supported by the Director of Authorisations and the Director of Operations.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThey ensure:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\