e budgetary controls are in place within the Authorisations Division, that services offer value for money, and in her absence, deputises for the CEO as the accounting officer.\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eFulfils the role of Project Leader/Programme Director/SRO as necessary, for example with implementing the Northern Ireland Protocol, and implementing new domestic legislation.\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eEnsures delivery of the VMD science strategy and being the VMD lead in liaison with the Veterinary Products Committee (independent advisory body to the VMD).\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eTakes full and proactive participation at VMD / Defra operational and strategic management meetings.\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eEnsures that the VMD has robust emergency response systems in place for contributing to wider supply chain considerations for veterinary medicines and also has in place mechanisms for dealing with more routine veterinary medicines supply issues.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2023-03-31T08:52:43Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Deputy Chief Executive Officer/Director of Authorisations, VMD","withdrawn":false}],"organisations":[{"analytics_identifier":"EA60","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/veterinary-medicines-directorate","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/veterinary-medicines-directorate","base_path":"/government/organisations/veterinary-medicines-directorate","content_id":"da332ae4-d021-4800-aa53-826058a46923","details":{"acronym":"VMD","brand":"department-for-environment-food-rural-affairs","default_news_image":{"high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5da99cfaed915d42a3e439fb/s960_VMD2017e.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5da99cfae5274a5cb0df8343/s300_VMD2017e.jpg"},"logo":{"crest":"single-identity","formatted_title":"Veterin